title: Views from the 404 | Ep. 22

description:
In this episode, DC and Karlous Miller talk music. From Drake's new album and all the feelings that come with it to DC's new solo efforts. DC and Karlous preview new tracks, "Grits In My Molly" and "I Got A Gun That Go Bring That Ass Here Boi." Young Fly and Lous also talk favorite female rappers and personal love for Rihanna. #85SouthShow
